INTRODUCTION
Play Swing Jetpack on your Google Chrome Browser with our simple & lightweight extension - No Internet required, no ADS, and 100% Free!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Swing Jetpack extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Swing Jetpack icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Swing Jetpack popup will open. Tap on the popup or press "Spacebar" to start ;)
That's all you need to do! Have fun!

HOW TO PLAY?
Tap the screen to swing the jetpack and avoid the obstacles
